.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.equals#system-object-equals(system-object-system-object)'>object.Equals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gethashcode'>object.GetHashCode()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.gettype'>object.GetType()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.memberwiseclone'>object.MemberwiseClone()</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.referenceequals'>object.ReferenceEquals(object?, object?)</a>\n</div>\n<div>\n<a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.object.tostring'>object.ToString()</a>\n</div>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Constructors</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.#ctor(System.Single)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.#ctor(System.Single)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape__ctor_System_Single_'>Shape(float)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L70'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Initializes a new instance of the <xref href=\"Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> class</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>protected Shape(float density)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>density</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The density</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Fields</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.Densit