opf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L86'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Get the number of child primitives.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public abstract int ChildCount { get; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.GetDensity' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.GetDensity' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_GetDensity'>GetDensity    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L93'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets or sets the density.\nChanging the density causes a recalculation of shape properties.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public float GetDensity { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.GetRadius' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.GetRadius' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_GetRadius'>GetRadius    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L107'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Radius of the Shape\nChanging the radius causes a recalculation of shape properties.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public float GetRadius { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.single'>float</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ShapeType' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ShapeType' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_ShapeType'>ShapeType    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L80'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Get the type of this shape.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public ShapeType ShapeType { get; internal set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.ShapeType.html'>ShapeType</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h2 class='section'>Methods</h2><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.Clone' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.Clone' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_Clone'>Clone()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L123'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Clone the concrete shape</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public abstract Shape Clone()</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Returns</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.html'>Shape</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">A clone of the shape</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ComputeAabb(Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Aabb@,Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.ControllerTransform@,System.Int32)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ComputeAabb(Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Aabb@,Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.ControllerTransform@,System.Int32)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_ComputeAabb_Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Aabb__Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_ControllerTransform__System_Int32_'>ComputeAabb(out Aabb, ref ControllerTransform, int)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L150'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Given a transform, compute the associated axis aligned bounding box for a child shape.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public abstract void ComputeAabb(out Aabb aabb, ref ControllerTransform controllerTransform, int childIndex)</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Parameters</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt><code>aabb</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Aabb.html'>Aabb</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The aabb results.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>controllerTransform</code> <a href='Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.ControllerTransform.html'>ControllerTransform</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The world transform of the shape.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt><code>childIndex</code> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.int32'>int</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">The child shape index.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ComputeProperties' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ComputeProperties' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_ComputeProperties'>ComputeProperties()    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L156'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Compute the mass properties of this shape using its dimensions and density.\nThe inertia tensor is computed about the local origin, not the centroid.</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>protected abstract void ComputeProperties()</code></pre><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ComputeSubmergedArea(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,System.Single,Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.ControllerTransform@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@)' data-commentId='M:Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.ComputeSubmergedArea(Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@,System.Single,Alis.Core.Physic.Dynamics.ControllerTransform@,Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Vector.Vector2F@)' id='Alis_Core_Physic_Collisions_Shapes_Shape_ComputeSubmergedArea_Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__System_Single_Alis_Core_Physic_Dynamics_ControllerTransform__Alis_Core_Aspect_Math_Vector_Vector2F__'>ComputeSubmergedArea(ref Vector2F, float, ref ControllerTransform, out Vector2F)    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/4_Operation/Physic/src/Collisions/Shapes/Shape.cs#L161'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Physic.Collisions.Shapes.Shape.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Used for the buoyancy controller</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>public abstract float ComputeSubmerged